+# v0 Validation Checklist
+
+## Before accepting generated output
+
+- [ ] Route intent is explicit (what page, who uses it, what state transitions exist)
+- [ ] Empty / loading / error states are implemented
+- [ ] Inputs have labels and validation handling
+- [ ] All generated paths are import-safe in `app/` or `src/app/`
+- [ ] Env keys are not hardcoded
+- [ ] Build passes (`npm run build`)
+- [ ] Lint and tests are green
+- [ ] Preview URL confirms responsive behavior
+
+## Post-import hardening
+
+- [ ] Replace ad-hoc theme usage with project token set
+- [ ] Confirm shadcn registry components compile with project config
+- [ ] Move custom utility or package config to deterministic files
+- [ ] Log any follow-up fixes as local tasks in small chunks
+
+## AI workflow health checks
+
+- [ ] Confirm whether chat context is still complete for continuation
+- [ ] Reconcile version history before destructive changes
+- [ ] Verify deployment IDs and branch links in Vercel dashboard
+


